1️⃣1️⃣ Running the Example Test
To run the tests , execute:
    pytest

Default behavior:
    1. Turns the chromium browser
    2. Tests run on headless mode
    3. Browswer will not open.

Test Results:
Results will appear in the terminal.
Example Output:
    2 passed

1️⃣2️⃣ Updating Playwright
To update playwright to the latest version , run:
    pip install pytest-playwright playwright -U

Meaning of -U
    -U means upgrade

